Here are other places where #region is used inside methods: Authorize in ExternalAuthorizer, FormatStockMessage in ProductExtensions, SearchProducts in ProductService, GetProductCount in ProductTagService, PrintOrdersToPdf in PdfService, DeleteGuestCustomers in CustomerService, InstallProducts in CodeFirstInstallationService, ProductListToHtmlTable in MessageTokenProvider. And the list can go on ...
